name: Blood Sugar (DenizMarul, Sagy, Fatih Emir Duran, Synthster)
name_original: Blood Sugar (DenizMarul, Sagy, Fatih Emir Duran, Synthster)
description:
Blood Sugar (DenizMarul, Sagy, Fatih Emir Duran, Synthster) is an action-shooter game developed by Sagy, DenizMarul and Fatih Emir Duran. It came out on 23-01-2022.
Blood Sugar (DenizMarul, Sagy, Fatih Emir Duran, Synthster) is available on PC. The game is sold via itch.io.
